 salmon, sliced (1 cm)","2 - 3 sprigs fresh parsley, leaves only","60 g red onions, quartered","30 g extra virgin olive oil, plus extra for greasing","20 g lemon juice","100 g pitted black olives","100 g baby leaf salad, mixed"]}],"id":"r131872","imageLink":"https:\/\/4.bp.blogspot.com\/-mlncK2b7brY\/XZVPsyaUssI\/AAAAAAAAc7o\/1a1S1aCVgMoUAJQtvo3oDh72NTTY3fuWgCLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_CpKAPMBNZdoCN7RG.png","title":"Smoked Salmon Pizza","publishedAt":"2016-09-12T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"33 g","fat":"36 g","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"95 g","calories":"3534 kJ \/ 845 kcal"},"usefulItems":"large bowl, cling film, 2 large baking trays, rolling pin, oven","basicInfo":["easy","10m","2h 30m","4 portions"]}